    body#page-top

        // Page loading
        #loading.d-flex.justify-content-center.align-items-center
            img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/loading.gif', alt='Loading gif')

        // Navigation
        nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.fixed-top
            .container.px-4
                a.navbar-brand(href='#page-top')
                    img(src='assets/img/navbar-logo.png', alt='Dragon Street')
                button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    | Menu
                    i.fas.fa-bars.ms-1
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse.justify-content-between
                    ul.navbar-nav.text-uppercase.mr-auto
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#masthead') Features
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#rarity') Rarity
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#roadmap') Roadmap
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#team') Team
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#faq') FAQ
                    .my-3.my-lg-0
                        a.btn.btn-default.btn-social(href='https://twitter.com/DragonStreetNFT', target='_blank')
                            i.fab.fa-twitter
                        a.btn.btn-default.btn-social(href='https://www.instagram.com/dragonstreetnft', target='_blank')
                            i.fab.fa-instagram
                        a.btn.btn-default.btn-social(href='!#', target='_blank')
                            i.fab.fa-discord
        // Masthead
        header#masthead.masthead
            .container
                .row.justify-content-end.mb-4
                    .col-md-4.col-sm-12
                        .masthead-subheading.text-uppercase Welcome To
                        img.img-fluid.mb-4(src='assets/img/masthead/welcome-logo.png', alt='Welcome')
                        p.text Brogons NFT collection of 10,000 randomly generated dragons wilding out in the streets of Ethereum Blockchain.
                        button.btn.btn-default(type='button')
                            img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/masthead/button-mint.png', alt='Mint')
                    .col-md-6.col-sm-12.d-flex.justify-content-end.mb-5
                        .masthead-giphy
                            img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/masthead/dragon.gif', alt='Dragon gif')
                #why-section.row.justify-content-center.p-5
                        .col-md-8.text-center
                            img.img-fluid.mb-2(src='assets/img/masthead/why-header.png', alt='Why')
                            p.text Aside from having the coolest avatar on the internet,
                            p.text When you join our community, our members have the ability to quickly access upcoming projects and participate in various exclusive giveaways for current and upcoming projects.
                            p.text We want to be more than just an NFT collection. Our goal is to create a long-term, community-oriented brand that benefits everyone as we grow. We will be reaching out to potential collaborators, influencers, and projects to continue to grow our metaverse and community while developing new Dragon Street brand projects.
                            p.text Join us and let us walk these streets together!

        // Rarity
        section#rarity.page-section.p-0
            .row
                each val in [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
                    .col.px-0
                        img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/portfolio/' + val + '.jpeg', alt='Portfolio item')
            .container.my-5
                .row
                    .col-lg-4.col-sm-6.mb-4
                        img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/rarity/unknown.png', alt='Rarity question mark')
                    .col-lg-8.col-sm-6.mb-4
                        img.img-fluid.mb-2(src='assets/img/rarity/header.png', alt='Rarity')
                        p.text Brogons are created through a random algorithm that ensures each brogon is unique and different from the others, as each reflects its own personality.
                        p.text It is no surprise that these dragons that roam the streets do so in their fashionable, vibrant outfits. Every Brogon is cool AF, but some possess very rare traits that set them apart from the rest. After all, not every dragon shoots rays from its eyes or has fur made of gold. And there are even more rare traits!
                        p.text There will also be special 1/1 editions of Brogons!
                        p.text We will be supported by Rarity Tools & Rarity Sniper post drop (see Roadmap).
            .row
                each val in [7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 12]
                    .col.px-0
